{"type": "article", "id": 19218, "title": "十字孔的墙面收纳", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-17T07:40:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 46, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016060712235498bLDuhaMrGFo5E3.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t伊朗的设计师 Navid Akbarnejad 做了这块带十字孔的插板，也是一个墙面收纳。可以插上挂钩，随意移动。它还有一些配套的模块，专门安装在盆景、画框、收纳盒等需要挂起来的小物品后面。后面的模块并没有做成十字孔，而是横条或者竖条相隔的，插进去后可以避免晃动。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145815QNVeCnmZ3UO7zYcT.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"700\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145816D8GHjgYvntfNLOPV.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"1041\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.99142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145816P5KyZB14sMRe3dVj.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"700\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}